#: ../../ACS.rst:132
msgid ""
"This is default clustering strategy used by Tigase ACS - MUC component. "
"In this strategy MUC rooms are partitioned so each room is hosted only on"
" one node. Every node contains full list of rooms with list of occupants "
"available in each room and map which contains room address as a key and "
"node as a value. If room is already opened (hosted) on some node, then "
"node hosting this room is resolved using map of room to node. In other "
"case node is selected by hash of room address using following algorithm"
